~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : wipe                                      ~FTPODnuts Revision
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : wipe [<roomname>] <number of message(s) from top>/all

   This wipes the message board.  Multiple messages can be wiped by 
   seperating the message number with a space.  If you specify "all" it
   wipes everything.

   eg: .wipe 2 8-10  will delete messages 2 and 8-10 from the board.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : read, write, search
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
